---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About · Dinakar Tumu">
  <section class="container prose">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <h2>Education and Early Life</h2>
    <p>
      I completed my master's degree at the New York Institute of Technology.
      After graduation, I lived in the Bay Area for about six years. During this
      time, I was interested in cycling, long walks, photography, and movies. I
      currently live in Bangalore.
    </p>

    <h2>Professional Journey</h2>
    <p>
      My professional journey began at a startup called Water, a sports league
      scoring app, where I developed iOS and Android applications using the Ionic
      framework. Building on that experience, I joined Liscio as a Founding
      Engineer. Over time, I transitioned to backend development and worked
      extensively with Ruby on Rails. One of the things I'm most proud of from my
      time there is building integrations, especially with Stripe and QuickBooks.
    </p>

    <h2>Current Role</h2>
    <p>
      Currently, I work as a Founding Engineer at
      <a href="https://pageloop.ai">Pageloop</a>. Although I initially joined in
      that role, I am now primarily focused on building AI agents, especially for
      automating screenshots and generating content updates.
    </p>

    <h2>Side Projects</h2>
    <p>
      In addition to my full-time work, I spend my free time working on a side
      project called Nostaliga.
    </p>

    <h2>Closing</h2>
    <p>That's a little about me.</p>

    <p class="muted">Reach me at <a href="mailto:dinakar@pageloop.ai">dinakar@pageloop.ai</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose a { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
